      "rationale": "Use error assessment is scoped out at MRL 2 for this COU. All simulations were executed by a single experienced analyst using a documented simulation plan and peer-reviewed input deck. Independent re-execution check was performed on one operating point confirming reproducibility. Formal use-error factor assessment is reserved for MRL 3+ submissions per project credibility plan."
